net.tfobz.vocabletrainer.data

Class VocableTrainerLocalization

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.tfobz.vocabletrainer.data.VocableTrainerLocalization

  • public class VocableTrainerLocalization
extends java.lang.Object
    Handles localization for the Vocable Trainer application by loading language-specific strings from YAML files and mapping them to application constants.
